Nanqing won't exist.

102
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,440
Nor will the world.

103
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:28,160
Pick me something fat.

104
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,950
Look at this. And this.

105
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,670
