But in these years,

159
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,110
my second brother Lin Gong is
the only one who treats me nicely.

160
00:09:54,910 --> 00:09:55,710
Whenever he saw

161
00:09:55,710 --> 00:09:56,960
