176
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:34,030
So emotionally,

177
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:36,590
I will take no side.

178
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,200
If one of them

179
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,670
