205
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:11,350
Uncle, step aside.

206
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:12,280
Go back.

207
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,670
So do you also think that

208
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,550
Teng Zijing's death

209
00:12:14,550 --> 00:12:15,760
