237
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:20,200
What are you doing?

238
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:22,110
Wait! My sheep!

239
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:37,150
Has Lin Gong left?

240
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:38,150
Yes.

241
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,640
